                    <span>This book is a must read for anyone who is seriously considering an Ebay business. It is written in a concise stype; there are no wasted words to struggle through. The information you will receive from this author is both up-to-date and of value.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">EBAYer MUST HAVE</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
